# The build only needs source + manifests; everything below is rebuilt in-image
# or must never enter the image (secrets, local state, VCS, dev artifacts).
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.git
**/.github
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store

# Secrets & local environment — never copy into an image layer.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/service-account*.json
**/gcp-*.json

# Local durable-state dir and scratch (disposable; Postgres is the real store).
**/.aaliyah
**/tmp
**/scratchpad

# Tests and editor cruft are not needed at runtime.
**/tests
**/.vscode
**/.idea
